Privacy policy 

Privacy Policy for [Baldwins Bot]

1. Introduction

Welcome to [Baldwins Bot]! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our Discord bot. By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

2. Information Collection and Use

We collect several types of information for various purposes to provide and improve our Service to you.

2.1 Types of Data Collected

2.1.1 User Data

	•	User ID: We collect your Discord user ID to identify you within our Service.
	•	Username and Discriminator: This is used to identify you uniquely in Discord.

2.1.2 Server Data

	•	Server ID: We collect the server ID where our bot is being used to provide server-specific features.
	•	Channel ID: This is used to identify specific channels for message handling.

2.2 How We Use Your Data

	•	To Provide and Maintain the Service: We use your data to operate and improve the bot’s functionality.
	•	To Notify You: We may use your information to notify you about updates or changes to our Service.
	•	To Provide Support: We use your information to provide customer support.

3. Data Storage and Security

We are committed to ensuring that your data is secure. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.

4. Data Sharing and Disclosure

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer to outside parties your Personally Identifiable Information. We may share your information only with:

	•	Service Providers: We may employ third-party companies to facilitate our Service, provide the Service on our behalf, perform Service-related services, or assist us in analyzing how our Service is used.
	•	Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.

5. Data Retention

We will retain your data only for as long as is necessary for the purposes set out in this Privacy
